ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F04%2F18%2Fphrases-to-avoid-on-your-resume-according-to-ex-google-recruiter.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNBC%20Make%20It%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20people%20should%20avoid%20sentences%20with%20more%20than%20'25%20words'.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20sentences%20should%20be%20less%20than%2025%20words%20maximum%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Church%20said.%20%26quot%3BProbably%20even%20shorter%20than%20that.%20Because%20the%20goal%20of%20a%20resume%20is%20for%20me%20to%20very%20quickly%20understand%20what%20you've%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20that%20recruiters%20have%20%26quot%3Bthree%20to%20five%20seconds%26quot%3B%20to%20go%20through%20each%20resume.%20%26quot%3BTime%20is%20the%20enemy%20in%20life%20and%20is%20the%20enemy%20in%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Google%20executive%20told%20the%20media%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BThe%20faster%20that%20we%20can%20move%2C%20the%20faster%20that%20we%20can%20solve%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmassive-red-flag-former-google-recruiter-shares-no-1-thing-to-avoid-in-a-job-interview-4631239%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BMassive%20Red%20Flag%26quot%3B%3A%20Former%20Google%20Recruiter%20Shares%20No.1%20Thing%20To%20Avoid%20In%20A%20Job%20Interview%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Church%20suggested%20that%20applicants%20should%20avoid%20a%20'word%20salad'%20of%20keywords.%20People%20tend%20to%20%26quot%3Bhave%20this%20word%20salad%20based%20off%20of%20what%20the%20%5Bjob%20description%5D%20says%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Church%20told%20CNBC%20Make%20It.%20If%20a%20marketing%20job%20requires%20candidates%20to%20implement%20strategic%20marketing%2C%20refine%20the%20company's%20messaging%20platforms%2C%20and%20engage%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20every%20one%20of%20those%20terms%20in%20one%20sentence%20would%20be%20a%20bad%20move%2C%20he%20added.%20Instead%2C%20Church%20recommended%20creating%20a%20rule%20when%20writing%20bullet%20points%20under%20job%20titles%3A%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20allowed%20to%20use%20more%20than%20one%20keyword%20in%20a%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplicants%20should%20avoid%20writing%20a%20list%20of%20tasks.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20give%20a%20s---%20about%20your%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20Church%20told%20the%20publication.%20The%20day-to-day%20duties%20of%20your%20job%20like%20emailing%20with%20your%20boss%20or%20creating%20your%20quarterly%20goals%20do%20not%20give%20a%20concrete%20sense%20of%20what%20you%20accomplished%20and%20how%20you%20helped%20the%20business%20move%20forward%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20one%20I%20see%20all%20the%20time%20that%20just%20blows%20my%20mind%20is%20'coordinated%20meetings%20with%20X'.%20There's%20no%20business%20impact%20for%20coordinating%20meetings%2C%26quot%3B%20Church%20told%20CNBC%20Make%20It.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Church%20highlighted%20the%20list%20of%20things%20they%20should%20have%20in%20their%20resumes.%20He%20said%20people%20should%20highlight%20what%20they%20did%20that%20benefitted%20the%20business%2C%20like%20getting%20new%20clients%20or%20exceeding%20sales%20goals%2C%20and%20use%20numbers%20to%20complement%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713932700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F19lupleg_resume_625x300_24_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fex-google-recruiter-reveals-resume-red-flags-shares-3-phrases-to-avoid-5510379%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nolan%20Church%2C%20CEO%20of%20salary%20data%20company%20FairComp%20and%20former%20recruiter%20for%20giants%20like%20Google%20and%20DoorDash%2C%20offers%20insights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fex-google-recruiter-reveals-resume-red-flags-shares-3-phrases-to-avoid-5510379%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv