uot%3BAmethi%20ki%20janta%20kare%20pukar%2C%20Robert%20Vadra%20ab%20ki%20baar%26quot%3B%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bthe%20people%20of%20Amethi%20want%20Robert%20Vadra%20this%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmethi%20votes%20on%20May%2020%20in%20the%20fifth%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20and%20the%20last%20day%20of%20filing%20nomination%20is%20May%203.%20While%20the%20BJP%20has%20announced%20sitting%20MP%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20as%20its%20candidate%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20yet%20to%20name%20its%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmethi%20has%20been%20a%20family%20seat%20for%20the%20Gandhis%2C%20represented%20in%20the%20past%20by%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20In%20the%202019%20election%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20victory%20over%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20managed%20to%20score%20a%20win%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad.%20This%20year%20too%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20contesting%20from%20Wayanad%2C%20which%20votes%20on%20Friday.%20With%20nominations%20for%20Amethi%20open%20till%20May%203%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20may%20file%20his%20papers%20after%20the%20polling%20in%20the%20Kerala%20seat.%20Recently%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20would%20be%20Congress's%20candidate%20in%20Amethi%20too.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20do%20whatever%20the%20party%20orders%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vadra%20has%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20sparked%20a%20buzz%20after%20he%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Amethi%20feel%20that%20if%20he%20contests%20there%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey'll%20have%20the%20option%20of%20correcting%20their%20mistake%20of%20electing%20Smritiji%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20they%20will%20ensure%20my%20victory%20by%20a%20huge%20margin%20if%20I%20contest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20earlier.%20Soon%20after%2C%20some%20posters%20demanding%20him%20as%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20started%20doing%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Irani%2C%20whose%20c