0stage%2C%20and%20a%20second%20large%20barn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20kitchen%20is%20a%20new%20addition%20to%20the%20residence%20that%20Leibovitz%20upgraded%2C%20featuring%20a%20subway%20tile%20backsplash%20and%20gas%20range.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20kitchen%20in%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66272dd40dfb1341e9fdd052%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20kitchen%20in%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%3Cp%3EJacob%20Elliott%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELeibovitz%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20had%20longed%20to%20find%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20make%20her%20home%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%2C%20and%20when%20she%20purchased%20the%20property%2C%20she%20thought%20she'd%20found%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20told%20of%20this%20extraordinary%20property%20that%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hill%20had%20views%20of%20the%20lagoon%20and%20bay%20and%20the%20coast%20that%20are%20magnificent.%20It%20has%20its%20own%20special%20climate%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20can%20grow%20year%20round.%20There%20were%2065%20acres%20with%20an%20old%20milking%20barn%20that%20Ansel%20Adams%20had%20photographed.%20It%20had%20been%20used%20as%20a%20gathering%20place%20for%20country%20and%20folk%20music%20concerts%20in%20its%20day.%20We%20planned%20to%20partner%20with%20a%20legendary%20farmer%20over%20the%20hill%20to%20bring%20the%20place%20back%20to%20its%20former%20self%20as%20a%20working%20and%20teaching%20farm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELeibovitz%20remodeled%20portions%20of%20the%20property%20but%20kept%20key%20fixtures%20like%20this%20rotary%20phone.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20rotary%20phone%20that%20still%20hangs%20on%20the%20wall%20in%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66272dd40dfb1341e9fdd051%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20rotary%20phone%20that%20still%20hangs%20on%20the%20wall%20in%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%3Cp%3EJacob%20Elliott%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20spent%20many%20holidays%20with%20friends%20in%20Bolinas%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20children%20were%20born%20we%20would%20go%20together%20and%20they%20would%20surf%20and%20pick%20up%20shells%20and%20stones%20along%20the%20shore.%20And%20I%20would%20occasionally%20look%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20her%20oldest%20daughter%20seemed%20to%20be%20eyeing%20colleges%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20Leibovitz%20snapped%20up%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthings%20don't%20always%20go%20as%20planned.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20three%20of%20my%20girls%20decided%20to%20go%20to%20college%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%26quot%3B%20prompting%20her%20to%20list%20the%20property%20for%20sale%20just%20five%20years%20later.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20weathered%20barn%20on%20the%20estate%20had%20previously%20been%20photographed%20by%20photographer%20Ansel%20Adams.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20barn%20on%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6628221f0dfb1341e9fe41a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20barn%20on%20Annie%20Leibovitz's%20California%20estate%3Cp%3EJacob%20Elliott%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAdams%20snapped%20a%20shot%20of%20a%20barn%20on%20the%20farm%20during%20his%20travels%20through%20the%20West%20in%201932%2C%20with%20one%20photo%20l