ow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20is%20holding%20the%20used%20litter%20tray%20of%20the%20Pull%20N%20Scoop%20litter%20box.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646f7242b379480018cbd6cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pull%20N'%20Scoop%20Litter%20Box%20had%20a%20disposable%20waste%20receptacle%20that%20required%20emptying%20every%20two%20to%20three%20rakes.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3ETo%20get%20more%20guidance%20on%20choosing%20the%20best%20self-cleaning%20cat%20litter%20boxes%2C%20we%20consulted%20four%20experts%20and%20used%20their%20criteria%20to%20narrow%20down%20our%20picks.%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetmed.vt.edu%2Fpeople%2Ffaculty%2Ffreeman-mark.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Mark%20Freeman%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20board-certified%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20community%20practice%20at%20Virginia-Maryland%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Leanne%20Lilly%20is%20a%20fear-free%20certified%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20behavioral%20medicine%20at%20The%20Ohio%20State%20University%20Veterinary%20Medical%20Center.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachel%20Geller%20is%20a%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20and%20retention%20specialist%20and%20founder%20of%20All%20Cats%20All%20the%20Time%2C%20Inc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrdenisejohnson.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Denise%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20fear-free%20certified%20veterinarian%20and%20cat%20behavior%20consultant%20(CCBC)%20at%20IndeVets%20who%20specializes%20in%20behavioral%20health%20and%20low-stress%20handling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20each%20litter%20b