%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-59474-20%26h%3Db68f0b6d73b4d542cb4816d207201e019903f34324f5d4d4cc42726231323954%26postID%3D646f6c9c8c8a4f19df34c7e6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-self-cleaning-litter-boxes%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fpetsafe-smart-wifi-enabled-covered%252Fdp%252F261382%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecovered%20with%20a%20front%20entry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20the%20model%20we%20recommend%20as%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-top-entry-litter-box%5C%22%3Ebest%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20tested%20the%20open%20design%2C%20which%20our%20experts%20prefer%20over%20covered%20litter%20boxes.%20All%20boxes%20have%20an%20entry%20point%20just%20over%206%20inches%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20which%20may%20be%20too%20high%20for%20some%20cats%20with%20mobility%20issues.%20My%20cats%20had%20never%20used%20crystal%20litter%20before%2C%20but%20they%20loved%20this%20box%20and%20used%20it%20without%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20ScoopFree%20litter%20box%20we%20tested%20arrived%20with%20a%20faulty%20safety%20sensor%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20issues%20with%20the%20replacement%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20self-cleaning%20litter%20box%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20cats%20are%20sitting%20beside%20the%20ScoopFree%20litter%20box%20and%20watching%20as%20the%20automated%20rake%20cleans%20the%20litter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646f7331b379480018cbd705%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20tester%20cats%20also%20closely%20observed%20the%20boxes'%20self-cleaning%20features.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20information%20from%20our%20experts%2C%20research%2C%20and%20testing%2C%20we%20recommend%20considering%20these%20essential%20features%20when%20choosing%20among%20the%20best%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccessibility%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20cats%20will%20need%20a%20more%20easily%20accessible%20box%20due%20to%20age%2C%20medical%20conditions%2C%20or%20mobility%20limitations.%20Geller%20suggests%20looking%20for%20a%20box%20with%20a%20ramp%20or%20ramp%20attachment%2C%20like%20the%20one%20you%20can%20purchase%20for%20Litter-Robot%203%20and%204.%20If%20your%20cat%20has%20mobility%20issues%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20skip%20the%20ScoopFree%20box.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.petsafe.net%2Fmedia%2Fmanuals%2FPAL00-14243_PAL00-14242_ScoopFree_Litter_Box_Manual.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanual%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20not%20intended%20for%20use%20by%20very%20senior%20cats%20or%20cats%20with%20physical%20limitations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20best%20litter%20box%20for%20your%20cat%20should%20be%201.5%20times%20their%20length%2C%20measured%20from%20their%20nose%20to%20tail%2C%20according%20to%20our%20experts.%20Although%20we%20prioritized%20litter%20boxes%20with%20spacious%20interiors%2C%20most%20automatic%20litter%20boxes%20simply%20aren't%20big%20enough%20for%20large%20breed%20cats%2C%20based%20on%20these%20size%20recommendations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELitter%20depth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cats%20have%20a%20natural%20instinct%20to%20dig%20and%20bury%20their%20waste%2C%20and%20they%20prefer%20at%20least%202%20to%203%20inches%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-litter%5C%22%3Ebest%20cat%20litter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20so%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrrachelcatbehavior.com%2Fabout-dr-rachel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERachel%20Geller%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20and%20retention%20specialist%20and%20founder%20of%20All%20Cats%20All%20the%20Time%2C%20Inc.%20However%2C%20we%20discovered%20that%20most%20automatic%20litter%20boxes%20offer%20a%20shallow%20litter%20depth.%20The%20CatGenie%20and%20ScoopFree%20models%20provide%20only%20an%20inch%20of%20substrate%20below%20their%20maximum%20fill%20line%2C%20while%20the%20Litter-Robot%20offers%20up%20to%202%20inches.%20If%20your%20cat%20prefers%20to%20dig%20in%20deep%20litter%2C%20an%20automatic%20box%20may%20not%20be%20ideal%20for%20their%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20assembly%20and%20cleaning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20testing%20boxes%2C%20we%20considered%20setup%20features%20like%20assembly%20time%2C%20user-friendly%20design%2C%20and%20the%20ease%20of%20routine%20cleaning.%20We%20also%20evaluated%20litter%20tracking%20and%20designs%20that%20minimize%20messes%20in%20the%20home.%20The%20best%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%20require%20minimal%20effort%20on%20your%20part.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Geller%20says%20a%20major%20drawback%20of%20automatic%20cat%20litter%20boxes%20is%20their%20price%20tag.%20These%20boxes%20don't%20come%20cheap.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20cat%20who%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20being%20picky%20about%20her%20box%2C%20an%20automatic%20litter%20box%20might%20be%20a%20failed%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20We%20tested%20automatic%20boxes%20at%20a%20range%20of%20price%20points%20and%20evaluated%20our%20selections%20with%20return%20policies%20and%20warranties%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20is%20holding%20the%20used%20litter%20tray%20of%20the%20Pull%20N%20Scoop%20litter%20box.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646f7242b379480018cbd6cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pull%20N'%20Scoop%20Litter%20Box%20had%20a%20disposable%20waste%20receptacle%20that%20required%20emptying%20every%20two%20to%20three%20rakes.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20more%20guidance%20on%20choosing%20the%20best%20self-cleaning%20cat%20litter%20boxes%2C%20we%20consulted%20four%20experts%20and%20used%20their%20criteria%20to%20narrow%20down%20our%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetmed.vt.edu%2Fpeople%2Ffaculty%2Ffreeman-mark.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Mark%20Freeman%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20board-certified%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20community%20practice%20at%20Virginia-Maryland%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Leanne%20Lilly%20is%20a%20fear-free%20certified%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20behavioral%20medicine%20at%20The%20Ohio%20State%20University%20Veterinary%20Medical%20Center.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachel%20Geller%20is%20a%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20and%20retention%20specialist%20and%20founder%20of%20All%20Cats%20All%20the%20Time%2C%20Inc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrdenisejohnson.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Denise%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20fear-free%20certified%20veterinarian%20and%20cat%20behavior%20consultant%20(CCBC)%20at%20IndeVets%20who%20specializes%20in%20behavioral%20health%20and%20low-stress%20handling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20each%20litter%20box%20for%20two%20weeks%2C%20assessing%20factors%20like%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20accessibility%2C%20noise%2C%20tracking%2C%20and%20overall%20cleaning%20efficiency.%20I%20stopped%20testing%20any%20boxes%20that%20weren't%20safe%20for%20my%20cats%20to%20use.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-59474-20%26h%3D642e9e01d9803f4d1b60940f5d26b6e87178a2449789fb531e38fd913d477e50%26postID%3D646f6c9c8c8a4f19df34c7e6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-self-cleaning-litter-boxes%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPet-Zone-Automatic-Filters-Cleaning%252Fdp%252FB00MA2T9BC%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPet%20Zone%20Smart%20Scoop%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20have%20safety%20features%2C%20so%20I%20eliminated%20it%20from%20testing%20shortly%20after%20setup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20evaluated%20how%20well%20each%20box%20performed%20its%20main%20functions%3A%20how%20often%20the%20box%20cleaned%20itself%2C%20if%20any%20waste%20remained%20after%20cleaning%2C%20how%20long%20the%20cleaning%20process%20lasted%2C%20and%20how%20often%20the%20litter%20box%20required%20maintenance.%20A%20daily%20sniff%20test%20determined%20whether%20the%20box%20kept%20odors%20under%20control.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20entry%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20gave%20higher%20consideration%20to%20litter%20boxes%20with%20accessible%20entrances%20%E2%80%94%20low-entry%20or%20a%20ramp%20or%20stairs%20%E2%80%94%20to%20suit%20small%20cats%20and%20seniors%20or%20mobility-impaired%20cats.%20I%20also%20observed%20my%20cats%20using%20the%20litter%20boxes%2C%20noting%20which%20entry%20point%20they%20chose%20and%20any%20hesitation%20associated%20with%20entering.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%20of%20the%20interior%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20interior%20of%20a%20litter%20box%20should%20be%20one%20and%20a%20half%20times%20the%20size%20of%20a%20cat%2C%20says%20Johnson.%20This%20length%20provides%20cats%20plenty%20of%20room%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20do%20their%20business.%20I%20gave%20higher%20consideration%20to%20boxes%20with%20larger%20interiors%20that%20could%20accommodate%20cats%20of%20different%20sizes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20sound%20of%20an%20automatic%20litter%20box%20could%20startle%20cats%2C%20resulting%20in%20them%20finding%20other%20places%20to%20urinate%20and%20defecate%2C%20Lilly%20explains.%20To%20test%20the%20noise%20level%20of%20each%20litter%20box%2C%20I%20downloaded%20the%20application%20%26quot%3BSound%20Meter%26quot%3B%20and%20recorded%20the%20maximum%20and%20average%20decibel%20rating%20of%20each%20litter%20box%20while%20it%20completed%20a%20full%20cycle.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDuring%20the%20testing%20period%2C%20I%20noted%20how%20much%20maintenance%20each%20litter%20box%20required.%20I%20also%20factored%20in%20any%20additional%20purchases%2C%20like%20special%20litter%2C%20waste%20bags%2C%20or%20cleaning%20supplies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20immediately%20removed%20from%20consideration%20any%20boxes%20that%20had%20faulty%20safety%20features%20or%20didn't%20come%20with%20safety%20features.%20I%20noted%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20safety%20features%20and%20documented%20if%20they%20worked%20as%20advertised.%20A%20noteworthy%20example%20is%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%2C%20which%20uses%20both%20motion-detecting%20lasers%20and%20weight-sensor%20technology%20to%20detect%20cats.%20The%20ScoopFree%20and%20CatGenie%20use%20motion-detecting%20lasers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20recorded%20how%20long%20it%20took%20to%20set%20up%20the%20litter%20box%20and%20whether%20I%20needed%20help%20from%20the%20user%20manual%2C%20app%2C%20or%20customer%20service.%20I%20also%20considered%20customer%20service%20accessibility%20and%20responsiveness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETracking%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDuring%20the%20two-week%20testing%20period%2C%20I%20collected%20loose%20litter%20on%20the%20floor%20to%20compare%20tracking%20volume.%20I%20also%20recorded%20how%20far%20away%20the%20litter%20ended%20up%20from%20the%20litter%20box.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExterior%20design%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20considered%20the%20size%20and%20aesthetic%20qualities%20of%20the%20litter%20box%2C%20focusing%20on%20features%20cat%20parents%20might%20consider%20important%20and%20visually%20appealing.%20Examples%20include%20modern%20and%20sleek%20design%2C%20color%20options%20to%20complement%20home%20decor%2C%20and%20quality%20materials.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAutomatic%20litter%20box%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20long-haired%20black%20and%20white%20cat%20is%20sitting%20on%20top%20of%20the%20CatGenie%20A.I.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646f7278d6d9d2001856e575%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20best%20self-cleaning%20litter%20box%20is%20one%20that%20your%20cat%20will%20use%20regularly.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20many%20litter%20boxes%20do%20I%20need%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20say%20to%20provide%20cats%20with%20at%20least%20one%20litter%20box%20per%20cat%2C%20plus%20an%20additional%20box%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20using%20automatic%20litter%20boxes%20that%20remove%20waste%20right%20away.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20every%20cat%20in%20the%20household%20to%20be%20able%20to%20eliminate%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Lilly.%20%26quot%3BOne%20extra%20is%20in%20case%20a%20cat%20prefers%20to%20urinate%20in%20one%20and%20defecate%20in%20the%20other%2C%20which%20isn't%20uncommon.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWill%20my%20cat%20use%20an%20automatic%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20cats%20will%20use%20an%20automatic%20box%20with%20the%20proper%20introduction%2C%20but%20some%20will%20never%20switch.%20It's%20important%20to%20consider%20your%20cat's%20personality%20and%20preferences%2C%20Geller%20says.%20Cats%20with%20a%20history%20of%20litter%20box%20selectiveness%20or%20skittish%20behavior%20may%20not%20want%20to%20use%20automatic%20boxes%2C%20and%20you'll%20want%20to%20offer%20a%20box%20your%20cat%20will%20comfortably%20use.%20Otherwise%2C%20you'll%20likely%20end%20up%20with%20regular%20messes%20outside%20the%20box.%20Additionally%2C%20Geller%20advises%20against%20placing%20litter%20boxes%20near%20startling%20sounds.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20might%20consider%20installing%20a%20CatGenie%20in%20a%20bathroom%20close%20to%20the%20rooms%20where%20you%20and%20your%20cats%20spend%20most%20of%20your%20time%20and%20away%20from%20noisy%20appliances%20like%20the%20washing%20machine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20can%20I%20get%20my%20cat%20to%20use%20an%20automatic%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGeller%20recommends%20introducing%20the%20new%20box%20slowly%20and%20with%20positive%20reinforcement.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20praise%20your%20cat%20and%20give%20them%20a%20treat%20when%20you%20see%20them%20checking%20out%20the%20box%20or%20interacting%20with%20it.%20Once%20your%20cat%20gets%20comfortable%20around%20the%20automatic%20litter%20box%2C%20add%20litter%20without%20turning%20on%20the%20self-cleaning%20function.%20Use%20a%20litter%20they're%20familiar%20with%20so%20they%20know%20exactly%20what%20the%20box%20is%20for.%20Then%2C%20begin%20by%20manually%20cycling%20it%20a%20few%20times%20a%20day%20while%20interacting%20with%20your%20cat%20in%20a%20way%20they%20enjoy.%20For%20example%2C%20pet%20them%20and%20praise%20them%20while%20operating%20the%20box.%20This%20can%20help%20desensitize%20them%20to%20the%20sound%20and%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20introduce%20my%20cat%20to%20an%20automatic%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20transition%20your%20cat%20to%20using%20an%20automatic%20box%2C%20Geller%20says%20to%20start%20by%20placing%20it%20near%20their%20old%20litter%20box.%20However%2C%20don't%20put%20any%20litter%20in%20yet.%20Allow%20your%20cat%20to%20explore%20the%20box%20on%20their%20own%20terms%2C%20and%20don't%20pick%20them%20up%20and%20place%20them%20inside.%20When%20you%20see%20your%20cat%20interacting%20with%20the%20litter%20box%2C%20praise%20them.%20After%20you%20add%20litter%20and%20your%20cat%20has%20used%20the%20box%20a%20few%20times%2C%20turn%20on%20the%20cleaning%20feature.%20Then%2C%20gradually%20move%20the%20traditional%20box%20farther%20away%20from%20the%20new%20one%20%E2%80%94%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20inches%20per%20day.%20During%20this%20transition%20period%2C%20Geller%20says%20to%20praise%20your%20cat%20for%20desired%20bathroom%20behaviors%20with%20treats%2C%20play%2C%20affection%2C%20or%20verbal%20praise.%20Only%20remove%20the%20old%20one%20once%20your%20cat%20uses%20the%20new%20box%20regularly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20vets%20recommend%20automatic%20litter%20boxes%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Johnson%2C%20cats%20have%20a%20natural%20instinct%20to%20hide%20eliminations%20and%20prefer%20boxes%20that%20reduce%20the%20chances%20of%20encountering%20another%20cat's%20waste.%20Automatic%20litter%20boxes%20remove%20waste%20after%20each%20use%20to%20quickly%20provide%20a%20clean%20litter%20box%2C%20but%20Lilly%20says%20they%20may%20not%20be%20ideal%20for%20cats%20with%20mobility%20issues%2C%20a%20history%20of%20litter%20box%20problems%2C%20or%20diseases%20that%20affect%20their%20urine%20or%20stool.%20In%20fact%2C%20monitoring%20elimination%20frequency%20and%20quality%20can%20be%20crucial%20to%20detecting%20feline%20health%20issues%20early.%20Whisker%20CEO%20and%20President%20Jacob%20Zuppke%20says%20technological%20updates%20planned%20for%20Litter-Robot%204%20may%20help%20address%20these%20concerns.%20For%20instance%2C%20AI-based%20behavioral%20learning%20can%20help%20track%20cats'%20bathroom%20habits.%20By%20analyzing%20data%20from%20litter%20box%20usage%2C%20the%20AI%20system%20learns%20each%20cat's%20unique%20patterns%20and%20habits%20and%20can%20alert%20you%20to%20changes%20that%20may%20suggest%20a%20health%20concern.%20That%20said%2C%20we%20didn't%20consider%20smart%20features%20like%20this%20when%20choosing%20the%20best%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20often%20do%20you%20have%20to%20clean%20an%20automatic%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Whisker%2C%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%20should%20be%20deep%20cleaned%20every%20one%20to%20three%20months.%20However%2C%20Freeman%20says%20cleaning%20litter%20boxes%20with%20soap%20and%20water%20every%20week%20or%20two%20is%20ideal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20automatic%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20automatic%20litter%20box%20is%20safe%2C%20accessible%2C%20and%20has%20an%20interior%20large%20enough%20for%20your%20cat%20to%20comfortably%20turn%20around%20and%20do%20their%20business.%20It%20should%20scoop%20and%20store%20waste%20with%20little%20odor%20and%20noise%2C%20and%20it%20shouldn't%20require%20much%20extra%20maintenance%20from%20you.%20For%20this%20guide%2C%20we%20selected%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%20as%20the%20best%20automatic%20litter%20box%20overall%20due%20to%20features%20like%20its%20spacious%20interior%2C%20quiet%20operation%2C%20accessibility%20features%2C%20and%20sleek%20design.%20We%20also%20included%20the%20budget-friendly%20PetSafe%20ScoopFree%20and%20the%20dust-free%20CatGenie.%20The%20best%20automatic%20litter%20box%20for%20you%20and%20your%20cat%20will%20depend%20on%20your%20budget%20and%20your%20cat's%20specific%20needs%20and%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%20work%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESelf-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%20keep%20boxes%20clean%20and%20prevent%20unpleasant%20household%20odors%20by%20using%20various%20mechanisms%20to%20remove%20waste.%20For%20example%2C%20Litter-Robot%204%20rotates%20a%20sifting%20cylinder%20to%20separate%20the%20waste%20from%20clean%20litter%20and%20deposits%20waste%20in%20an%20odor-trapping%20drawer.%20CatGenie%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20flushes%20away%20waste%20and%20uses%20washable%20granules%20as%20litter.%20The%20ScoopFree%20box%