2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnever-off-duty-british-police-officers-catch-suspected-thief-while-on-stag-do-in-barcelona-13121302%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnever-off-duty-british-police-officers-catch-suspected-thief-while-on-stag-do-in-barcelona-13121302%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnever-off-duty-british-police-officers-catch-suspected-thief-while-on-stag-do-in-barcelona-13121302%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MDH%20%26amp%3B%20Everest%20Spice%20Row%20Explained%3A%20How%20to%20Read%20Ingredients%20on%20Masala%20Packets%3F%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDo%20store-bought%20%3Cem%3Emasalas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spices)%20contain%20a%20cancer-causing%20substance%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Singapore%20placed%20four%20masalas%20from%20MDH%20and%20Everest%20under%20the%20scanner%2C%20food%20safety%20regulator%20FSSAI%20(Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India)%20will%20now%20conduct%20quality%20checks%20on%20products%20of%20these%20two%20popular%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347211%2Fhow-to-grow-spices-at-home-dr-anshu-tripathi-shares-tips-garden-uttarakhand-roorkee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espice%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%205%20April%2C%20Hong%20Kong%E2%80%99s%20food%20safety%20regulator%2C%20The%20Centre%20for%20Food%20Safety%20(CFS)%20found%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20pesticide%2C%20ethylene%20oxide%20in%20these%20masalas.%20The%20US%20EPA%20(Environmental%20Protection%20Agency)%20states%20that%20ethylene%20oxide%20is%20carcinogenic%20and%20can%20cause%20cancer%20through%20long-term%20exposure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20masalas%20under%20contention%20are%20MDH%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Madras%20Curry%20Powder%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Sambhar%20Masala%20Powder%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Curry%20Powder%E2%80%99%20and%20Everest%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Fish%20Curry%20Masala%E2%80%99%20.%20The%20Singapore%20Food%20Agency%20found%20the%20pesticide%20in%20Everest%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Fish%20Curry%20Masala%E2%80%99%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20FSSAI%20has%20started%20taking%20samples%20of%20various%20spices%20from%20the%20market%20to%20check%20their%20quality%20and%20presence%20of%20the%20cancer-causing%20chemical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20current%20development%2C%20FSSAI%20has%20taken%20samples%20of%20spices%20of%20all%20brands%2C%20including%20MDH%20and%20Everest%2C%20from%20the%20market%20to%20check%20whether%20they%20meet%20the%20FSSAI%20norms%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20guide%20on%20how%20you%20can%20safeguard%20yourself%20and%20know%20what%20you%20consume.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20ethylene%20oxide%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20routine%20surveillance%2C%20the%20CFS%20collected%20the%20said%20MDH%20and%20Everest%20masala%20samples%20from%20three%20retail%20outlets%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20discovery%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%E2%80%99s%20presence%20above%20the%20permissible%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESFA%20has%20directed%20the%20recall%20of%20Everest's%20Masala%20Fish%20Curry%20from%20India%20due%20to%20exceeding%20levels%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%20detected%20in%20the%20product.%20The%20recall%20is%20ongoing.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmEDarMptR5%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmEDarMptR5%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6UnFtZUGQ6%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6UnFtZUGQ6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Singapore%20Food%20Agency%20(SFA)%20(%40SGFoodAgency)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSGFoodAgency%2Fstatus%2F1780815010174034401%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfs.gov.hk%2Fenglish%2Fpress%2F20240405_10919.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20adds%20that%20The%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer%20has%20classified%20ethylene%20oxide%20as%20a%20Group%201%20carcinogen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthylene%20oxide%20is%20an%20organic%20compound%20used%20primarily%20to%20produce%20other%20chemicals%2C%20and%20is%20also%20used%20as%20a%20sterilising%20agent%20for%20medical%20equipment%2C%20pesticide%20and%20a%20fumigating%20agent%20for%20spices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20presence%20lends%20a%20longer%20shelf%20life%20to%20food%20products.%20The%20EPA%20states%20that%20%E2%80%98ethylene%20oxide%20is%20carcinogenic%20to%20humans%20by%20the%20inhalation%20route%20of%20exposure%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20lymphoid%20and%20breast%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20CFS%20found%20the%20presence%20of%20this%20carcinogen%2C%20it%20instructed%20the%20vendors%20to%20remove%20the%20products%20from%20the%20shelves%20and%20asked%20the%20concerned%20distributors%20and%20importers%20to%20recall%20the%20affected%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20asked%20consumers%20not%20to%20buy%20the%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Singapore%20Food%20Agency%20has%20directed%20a%20recall%20of%20the%20products.%20Its%20report%20states%20that%20while%20ethylene%20oxide%20is%20allowed%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20sterilisation%20of%20spices%2C%20here%20its%20presence%20is%20above%20the%20accepted%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20there%20is%20no%20immediate%20risk%20to%20consumption%20of%20food%20contaminated%20with%20low%20levels%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%2C%20long%20term%20exposure%20may%20lead%20to%20health%20issues.%20Therefore%2C%20exposure%20to%20this%20substance%20should%20be%20minimised%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfa.gov.sg%2Fdocs%2Fdefault-source%2Faccredited-overseas-attachments%2F180424-media-release---recall-of-everest%2527s-masala-fish-curry.pdf%3Fsfvrsn%3De0a4f694_1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20read%20food%2Fingredient%20labels%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20news%20comes%20on%20the%20back%20of%20finding%20that%20Nestle%20adds%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347926%2Fcerelac-sugar-nestle-babies-infants-health-nutrition-report-meal-plan-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esugar%20in%20Cerelac%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20directing%20e-commerce%20firms%20to%20remove%20Bournvita%20and%20other%20such%20drinks%20from%20the%20health%20drinks%20category%2C%20this%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20consumers%20to%20be%20more%20alert%20and%20look%20at%20food%20labels%20before%20buying%20any%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6F_0IzN8Hr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6F_0IzN8Hr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3