0sulphur%2C%20and%20magnesium%2C%20and%20tertiary%20nutrients%20like%20iron%2C%20zinc%2C%20manganese%2C%20copper%2C%20boron%2C%20molybdenum%2C%20and%20chlorine.%20These%20elements%20act%20as%20an%20essential%20catalyst%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20knew%20the%20technique%20to%20give%20these%20nutrients%20via%20water%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20the%20ratio%20in%20which%20these%20elements%20were%20required%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20crop.%20The%20training%20helped%20me%20learn%20the%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Within%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWithin%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries.%20Photo%3A%20Pixabay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5x%20more%20produce%20in%20small%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%2C%20Dheeraj%20established%20a%203%2C500%20sq%20ft%20hydroponics%20set-up%20on%20his%20farm.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20planted%209%2C000%20saplings%20of%20strawberries%20using%20coco%20peat%20as%20a%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20grow%20bags%20and%20filled%20them%20with%20cocopeat.%20In%20these%20grow%20bags%2C%20I%20connected%20four%20drippers%20for%20water%20supply%20and%20made%20four%20small%20holes%20for%20drainage.%20Next%2C%20I%20planted%20the%20saplings%20and%20supplied%20all%20the%20nutrients%20to%20the%20crop%20with%20water.%20With%20this%20method%2C%20I%20water%20the%20plant%20at%20a%20gap%20of%20a%20week%2C%20instead%20of%20running%20the%20water%20supply%2024%C3%977.%20Almost%2070%20percent%20of%20water%20gets%20absorbed%20in%20the%20media%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Dheeraj%201.5%20months%20and%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20to%20build%20the%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20was%20all%20worth%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20one-time%20investment%20that%20reduces%20the%20overall%20input%20costs%20after%20a%20certain%20period.%20For%20five%20years%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries%20and%20earned%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20the%20same%20period.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20method%20is%20far%20better%20than%20conventional%20farming.%20With%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20got%20five%20times%20more%20production%20in%20hydroponics%20compared%20to%20open-land%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20tasks%20farmers%20should%20be%20mindful%20of%20while%20adopting%20this%20method%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20need%20to%20monitor%20the%20hydroponics%20farm%20at%20least%20once%20every%20day.%20The%20strawberries%20are%20heavily%20attacked%20by%20pests%20and%20fungu