0or%20a%20copper%20%3Cem%3Elota%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spherical%20vessel).%20Keep%20the%20content%20for%20at%20least%2015%C2%A0%20days%20until%20the%20content%20becomes%20completely%20blue.%20Take%202%20ml%20of%20this%20mixture%20and%20dilute%20it%20in%201%20litre%20of%20water.%20Spray%20the%20diluted%20content%20on%20crops%20once%20every%20week%20throughout%20the%20season.%20This%20tackles%20fungi%20attack%20and%20gives%20a%20good%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20am%20extremely%20happy%20to%20reap%20benefits%20by%20adopting%20this%20new%20technique%2C%20initially%20I%20made%20some%20mistakes%20in%20getting%20good%20nutrients%20from%20the%20market.%20I%20got%20misled%20into%20buying%20nutrients%20from%20fraud%20companies.%20This%20delayed%20my%20production%20by%201.5%20months.%20But%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20the%20next%20season%20from%20the%20same%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dheeraj%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20cultivating%20red%20and%20yellow%20varieties%20of%20capsicum%20on%20the%20hydroponics%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20his%20example%2C%20Dheeraj%20advises%20other%20farmers%20to%20explore%20hydroponics%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20technique%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%20any%20untutored%20farmer%20can%20reap%20handsome%20profits%20with%20hydroponics%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Dheeraj%20Verma.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713767578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-1-1713533722.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Encouraged%20by%20the%20soil-less%20farming%20technique%20used%20in%20Israel%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Dheeraj%20Verma%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20strawberries%20u