e%20process%20of%20evaporative%20cooling%20to%20release%20a%20gentle%2C%20refreshing%20breeze%20into%20the%20living%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20re-adaptation%20of%20traditional%20methods%2C%20combining%20ancient%20systems%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F187517%2Flifestyle-eco-friendly-cooling-solution-without-ac-sustainable-homes-architect-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodern%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20are%20opening%20buildings%20to%20nature%20instead%20of%20building%20installations%20for%20conventional%20urban%20structures%20that%20shut%20their%20inhabitants%20into%20these%20closed%20boxes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Monish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20observed%20that%20this%20structure%20can%20comfortably%20reduce%20the%20temperature%20up%20to%2030%20degrees%20Celsius.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20factory%2C%20we%20reduced%20the%20temperature%20from%2045-47%20to%2032%20degrees%20Celsius%20because%20the%20water%20temperature%20was%2026-27%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Monish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20CoolAnt%20was%20among%20the%2012%20winners%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Low-Carbon%20Lifestyles%20Challenge.%20It%20bagged%20a%20%2410%2C000%20grant%20from%20the%20UN%20Environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELearn%20how%20CoolAnt%20is%20helping%20homes%20and%20commercial%20establishments%20reduce%20their%20power%20load%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FQL-RhECqv_U%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load