3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20ink%20touches%20the%20surface%20of%20our%20skin%2C%20the%20silver%20nitrate%20reacts%20with%20the%20natural%20salts%20in%20our%20body%20and%20turns%20into%20silver%20chloride.%20This%20reaction%20happens%20in%20just%2040%20seconds!%20Once%20the%20silver%20chloride%20is%20formed%2C%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20washed%20away%20with%20water%20and%20can%20remain%20on%20the%20skin%20for%202%20to%2030%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20silver%20nitrate%20in%20the%20ink%20is%20between%207%20to%2025%20percent%20but%20the%20exact%20amount%20is%20never%20revealed%20by%20the%20government.%20Also%20known%20as%20the%20indelible%20ink%2C%20it%20was%20first%20made%20by%20the%20National%20Physical%20Laboratory%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sole%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20ink%20has%20been%20Mysore%20Paints%20and%20Varnish%20Limited.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F137858%2Felection-commission-beggars-homeless-undertrials-poll-process%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Election%20Commission%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20ordered%20more%20than%2026%20lakh%20vials%20for%20the%20election%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20a%20single%20vile%20of%2010%20mg%20can%20cover%20as%20many%20as%20700%20voters.%20A%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EFirst%20Post%20%3C%2Fem%3Estates%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20buying%20this%20ink%20is%20Rs%2055%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713525467000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347774%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elections%202024%3A%20The%20voter%20ink%20or%20the%20indelible%20ink%20can%20stay%20on%20a%20voter's%20finger%20anywhere%20between%202%20to%2030%20days.%20Here's%20what%20it%20is%20made%20of!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347774%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-voting-ink-indelible-mark-facts-to-know-before-voting%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98There%E2%80%99s%20No%20Age%20Limit%20For%20Learning%E2%80%99%3A%20Started%20at%2063%2C%20Woman%20Earns%20Lakhs%20Growing%20Saffron%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202023%2C%20Shubha%20Bhatnagar%20initiated%20a%20rather%20interesting%20dinner%20table%20conversation.%20She%20shared%20her%20dream%20of%20cultivating%20saffron%20indoors%20and%20providing%20employment%20to%20rural%20women%20in%20the%20nearby%20villages.%20A%20homemaker%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335137%2Fsenior-citizens-travel-life-after-retirement-trekking-riding-travelling-biking-road-trips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E63-year-old%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20of%20responsibilities%E2%80%9D%20and%20wished%20to%20embark%20upon%20a%20journey%20of%20self-reliance%20by%20becoming%20an%20agriprenuer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20dinner%20table%20were%20two%20engineers%3A%20her%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20cold%20storage%20business.%20They%20were%20intrigued%20by%20her%20idea%20and%20immediately%20started%20looking%20at%20how%20to%20make%20her%20vision%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20in%20the%20following%20weeks%20and%20months%20that%20followed%20were%20no%20longer%20about%20the%20everyday%20mundanities%2C%20but%20rather%20about%20how%20saffron%20could%20be%20cultivated%20indoors%20and%20how%20they%20could%20achieve%20the%20necessary%20climatic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaffron%2C%20a%20highly%20valued%20spice%2C%20is%20exclusively%20grown%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20benefiting%20from%20its%20unique%20soil%20and%20weather%20conditions.%20Through%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20they%20replicated%20the%20climatic%20conditions%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20a%20cold%20storage%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%20using%20IoT%20(Internet%20Of%20Things).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20by%20integrating%20technology%2C%20they%20planted%20the%20authentically%20sourced%20seeds%20in%20the%20cold%20storage%20chamber%20in%20August%202023%2C%20yielding%20their%20first%20harvest%20approximately%20three%20months%20later.%20Named%20%E2%80%98Shubhavni%20SmartFarms%2C%E2%80%99%20they%20commenced%20selling%20their%20first%20produce%20of%20two%20kilograms%20of%20saffron%20earlier%20this%20year.%20They%20have%20sold%20over%20Rs%208%20lakh%20worth%20of%20saffron%20and%20employed%2025%20women%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Shubha%20achieved%20this%20remarkable%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20business%20trip%20to%20Kashmir%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20MA%20(Master%20of%20Arts)%20in%20Hindi%20from%20Shikohabad%2C%20Shubha%20got%20married%20and%20moved%20to%20Mainpuri.%20She%20spent%20the%20next%2040%20years%20of%20her%20life%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20two%20children%3A%20a%20son%20and%20daughter%2C%20and%20later%20her%20grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shubha%20started%20growing%20saffron%20indoors%20last%20year%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-