ace%20needed%20for%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CA%20farmer%20would%20typically%20sow%202%2C000%20kg%20of%20saffron%20in%201.5%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20while%20we%20are%20able%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20560%20square%20feet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ankit%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubha%20wants%20to%20create%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338349%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-with-aeroponics-online-classes-himachal-pradesh-solan-mushrooms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaffron%20%E2%80%9Crevolution%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20help%20more%20people%20grow%20the%20spice%20indoors.%20Through%20her%20venture%2C%20she%20is%20currently%20providing%20employment%20to%20over%2020%20women%20in%20Mainpuri%2C%20as%20the%20process%20of%20growing%20saffron%20is%20laborious.%20Right%20from%20drying%20the%20bulbs%20to%20plucking%20each%20stigma%2C%20drying%2C%20and%20packing%20them%2C%20it%20requires%20careful%20and%20precise%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Geeta%20Devi%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20dependable%20income.%20At%2040%20years%20old%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20a%20mother%20of%20five%20and%20the%20primary%20provider%20for%20her%20family.%20Previously%2C%20she%20laboured%20in%20the%20fields%20under%20the%20scorching%20sun%2C%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Work%20was%20inconsistent%2C%20and%20income%20was%20meagre%2C%20she%20recalls.%20However%2C%20since%20joining%20Shubhavni%20Farms%20last%20July%2C%20her%20situation%20has%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20enjoy%20the%20work%20here%20and%20brought%20in%2020%20more%20women.%20We%20were%20taught%20everything%20about%20saffron%20cultivation%20and%20did%20everything%20from%20aeration%20to%20keeping%20it%20clean%20and%20removing%20the%20stamen%20from%20the%20flower.%20We%20are%20working%20in%20a%20comfortable%20environment%20instead%20of%20bearing%20the%20harsh%20heat.%20We%20get%20paid%20at%20least%20Rs%20100%20more%20per%20day%2C%E2%8